                <p class="mb-8">Subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive deals and Austin travel tips</p>
                <form class="flex gap-4">
                    <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-gray-900">
